    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I've pampered this car since day one, and it's still in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or even a speck of dust to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall head-over-heels the second they start the engine. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
