      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive benchmark in atmospheric performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is routed through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential, providing unparalleled mechanical feedback. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe and a pristine chassis, retaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. The exterior maintains its deep luster with no signs of oxidation, while the interior boasts supple Nappa leather and functional side bolsters. This is a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle with zero deferred maintenance, offering the raw, analog driving experience that modern iterations lack.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
