    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless Deep Obsidian finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent, with the hand-stitched leather upholstery showing no signs of creasing or wear. Every electronic component, from the premium surround-sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car has been pampered, stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained exclusively at certified dealerships with a comprehensive binder of service records included. With exceptionally low mileage and a spotless undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
